name: Oval Earrings ~ Pearl Within
description:
Hand-formed ovals of Sterling or Gold-fill, enclose teardrop shaped Freshwater Pearls. A classic and elegant design.

*Available in white or raven.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Oval Earrings ~ Pearl Below
description:
Hand-formed ovals of Sterling or Gold-fill, rest atop teardrop shaped Freshwater Pearls. A classic and elegant design.

*Available in white or raven.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Oval Earrings ~ Double Pearl
description:
Hand-formed ovals of Sterling or Gold-fill, enclose teardrop shaped Freshwater Pearls, while a second pearl dangles beneath. 
A classic and elegant design.

*Available in white or raven.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Layered Oval Earrings ~ Onyx
description:
Onyx abacus beads rest between overlapping metal ovals. Three onyx stones dangle at varying lengths from the bottom, adding interest and movement.

Available in sterling silver or 14K gold-fill.

name: Layered Oval Earrings ~ Pearl
description:
Freshwater pearls rest between overlapping metal ovals. Three pearls dangle at varying lengths from the bottom, adding interest and movement.

*Available in Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Small Shell Earrings ~ Pearl
description:
A smaller version of the shell earring that's every bit as charming. Inspired by the form of a nautilus shell, sterling or gold-filled wire is hand-formed into an intertwining spiral design. Freshwater pearls lend an extra touch of softness to these feminine earrings.

*Available in white or raven pearls.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Shell Earrings ~ Pearl
description:
Reminiscent of a nautilus shell, sterling or gold-filled wire is hand-formed into an intertwining spiral design. High grade freshwater pearls lend an extra touch of softness to these feminine earrings. 

*Available in white, gray or raven pearls.

name: Shell Earrings ~ Turquoise
description:
Hand-formed wire intertwines to create a playful spiral design. Striking turquoise stones add a pop of color.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Oval Swarovski Drops
description:
Hand-formed ovals of sterling silver or 14K gold-fill, surround brilliant Swarovski crystals that beautifully catch the light. 

*Available in: clear, beige, aqua, purple and amber.

name: Slender Twist Earrings ~ Swarovski Crystals
description:
Delicate twists of sterling or gold-filled wire, catch shimmering Swarovski crystals in their bend. 
Slight and graceful earrings with a touch of sparkle.

*Available in: clear, beige, aqua, purple, and amber. 

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled

name: Twist Earrings ~ Swarovski Crystals
description:
Twists of sterling or gold-filled wire, catch shimmering Swarovski crystals in their bend. 
Graceful earrings with a touch of sparkle.

*Available in: clear and beige

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled

name: Heart Twist Earrings ~ Swarovski Crystals
description:
Twists of sterling or gold-filled wire, catch radiant Swarovski Crystal hearts in their bend. 

Graceful earrings with lots of sparkle.

*Available in: clear, aqua and crimson.

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled

name: Triple Hoop Onyx Earrings
description:
Sterling or 14K gold-filled wire, circles gleaming onyx teardrops three times around. A classic look that is delicate though not too dainty.

These earrings look great with their matching necklace.

name: Raindrop Earrings ~ Light
description:
Tiny glass droplets align on sterling or gold-filled rings, like raindrops on a rain chain. An Aurora borealis coating on the glass allows it to shimmer in the light.

*Light colors: clear, gray, and green.

name: Raindrop Earrings ~ Dark
description:
Tiny glass droplets align on sterling or gold-filled rings, like raindrops on a rain chain. An Aurora borealis coating on the glass allows it to shimmer in the light.

Dark colors: blue, purple and black.

name: Swing Earrings
description:
Hand-formed wire paired with colorful gemstones to sway playfully from the ears. 

Available in: faceted Mother of Pearl, Amazonite, Aventurine, Carnelian and Onyx

name: Mini Oval Earrings
description:
Simple and sweet. A tiny wire oval to adorn your ears.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.

name: Oval Earrings
description:
Simple and sweet, Sterling or 14K Gold-filled ovals dangle from ear wires of the same.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled

name: Inside Out Oval Earrings
description:
Simple and sweet, hand-formed ovals enclose smaller versions of themselves. 

*Sterling, 14K Gold-filled or a combination of the two.

name: Double Link Oval Earrings
description:
The flattering oval form gains length from a second oval linked below.
A simple and elegant design.

*Sterling or 14K gold-filled.

name: Shell Necklace ~ Freshwater Pearls
description:
A spiral pendant is hand-formed of sterling or gold-filled wire. Freshwater pearls are placed within the intertwining design that is reminiscent of a nautilus shell.  

*Chain measures 17" with a 2" extender.

*Available in: white, gray or raven.

* Sterling silver or 14K gold-filled.

name: Shell Necklace ~ Turquoise
description:
A slight variation on the popular shell design, featuring turquoise stones.

*Sterling or 14K Gold-filled.
*17" with a 2" extender.

name: Layered Oval Necklace ~ Pearl
description:
Three hand-formed sterling or gold-filled ovals, overlap each other, forming a delicate, layered pendant. Small freshwater pearls add interest and movement to the design.

*Available in Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled.

*Chain measures 17" with a 2" extender.

name: Layered Oval Necklace ~ Onyx
description:
Three hand-formed sterling or gold-filled ovals, overlap each other, forming a delicate, layered pendant. Small onyx stones add interest and movement to the design.

*Available in Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled.

*Chain measures 17" with a 2" extender.

name: Raindrop Necklace ~ Light
description:
Glass droplets succeed one another on a delicate chain, clustering in the center and trailing off at the end. Luminous, like drops of water in the sunlight. 

Light colors: clear, gray and green.

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled.

*Both the Sterling and Gold-filled chains are lightly textured and measure 17" with a 2" extender.

name: Raindrop Necklace ~ Dark
description:
Glass droplets succeed one another on a delicate chain, clustering in the center and trailing off at the end. Luminous, like drops of water in the sunlight. 

*Dark colors: blue, purple and black.

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-filled.

*Both the Sterling and Gold-filled chains are lightly textured and measure 17" with a 2" extender.

name: Scallop Necklace ~ Garnet
description:
Faceted Garnets form a procession at the center of a delicate cable chain.
An elegant necklace with plenty of shimmer.

Available in Bright Sterling, Oxidized Sterling and 14K Gold-filled.

*Chain measures 16" with a 2" extender.

name: Scallop Necklace ~ Apatite
description:
Faceted Apatite form a procession at the center of a delicate cable chain. 
An elegant necklace with plenty of shimmer.

Available in Sterling Silver and 14K Gold-filled.

Chain measures 16" with a 2" extender.

name: Scallop Necklace ~ Seed Pearls
description:
Small seed pearls form a gentle slope at the center of a delicate cable chain. 

*Available in soft pink or white.

*Sterling or 14K gold-fill.

*Chain measures 16" with a 2" extender.

name: Scallop Necklace ~ Medium Rice Pearls
description:
A procession of freshwater pearls rests at the center of a delicate cable chain. 

*Chain measures 16" with a 2" extender.

*Available in white or raven.

*Sterling Silver or 14K Gold-fill.

name: Scallop Necklace ~ Large Rice Pearls
description:
Rice-shaped freshwater pearls create a gentle arc at the center of a delicate cable chain.

*Chain measures 16" with a 2" extender.

*Available in white and raven. 

*Sterling or 14K gold-filled.

name: Brass Heart Necklace
description:
Winding heart pendant of brass features a white teardrop pearl. 
Both suspend from a 14K gold-fill chain that adjusts from 18" to 20".

*Different length chain available upon request.

name: Button Pearl Bracelet
description:
Luminous button pearls zig zag along the length of this sweet bracelet.
Finished with a lobster claw clasp and three rings for length flexibility.

*Choose between white, mauve and gray.

*Available in sterling silver or 14k gold fill.

name: Circle Link Bracelet
description:
Round wire is hand-formed into circles, each linking to another.
Finished with a large lobster claw clasp.

name: Oval Link Bracelet
description:
Round wire is hand-formed into ovals that cleverly link to one another, forming a continuous strand around the wrist.
Finished with a large lobster claw clasp and several rings that allow the length to adjust.

*Available in sterling silver, 14k gold-fill, or an alternating combination of the two.

name: Infinity Bracelet
description:
Round wire is looped and wrapped into the symbol for eternity, then linked end to end to form a continuous strand around the wrist. 
Finished with a large lobster claw clasp and three rings, allowing the length to adjust from ..... to .....

*Available in sterling silver, 14k gold-fill, or an alternating combination of both.
